                  </persName>
            . I am in the prosecutor's employ - I was at work - the prisoner did not purchase any thing - I went out and saw him throw the caddy at the prosecutor's feet.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was passing along - I observed a man put this caddy by the side of a door - I waited a few minutes, and, as no one came, I took it up.(
